<h2 id='reporting-a-specific-question'>Reporting a Specific Question</h2><pre class="highlight shell tab-shell"><code>curl <span class="s2">"https://community.tribe.so/api/v1/questions/5a816275f8030b3bdd655b0d/reports"</span>
  -X POST
  -H <span class="s2">"Authorization: Bearer {access_token}"</span>
</code></pre>
<p>This endpoint reports (flags) a specific question to admins and moderators.</p>
<h3 id='http-request-16'>HTTP Request</h3>
<p><code class="request">POST /api/v1/questions/:id/reports</code></p>
